WEBVTT
Kind: captions
Language: en

00:00:03.827 --> 00:00:04.947
Well, good evening, family.

00:00:04.947 --> 00:00:06.725
Thank you for joining me again today.

00:00:06.980 --> 00:00:15.630
We're going to go ahead and pray, and then go over some of the things the Lord showed us yesterday in prayer.

00:00:17.697 --> 00:00:27.406
It's been amazing praying over President Trump and the Valley of Decision concerning where we are as a nation.

00:00:34.869 --> 00:00:36.820
As yesterday's prayer time ended, I had more time praying and talking to the Lord about it.

00:00:47.050 --> 00:01:03.359
He took the puzzle pieces of everything we have been praying over since October and started putting them together regarding where we are in the Valley of Decision concerning President Trump and the decisions he's making.

00:01:03.799 --> 00:01:17.080
He even stated that he is a businessman before he is the president, which I thought was an interesting statement because he is running it like a business.

00:01:17.451 --> 00:01:40.280
The decisions he's making are strategic in his mind, like the chess match I saw him playing—how to dominate world markets and the world economy, not for mercy, but to make America great.

00:01:42.255 --> 00:01:46.453
Just like he has said over and over again, he's not thinking about other nations.

00:01:46.453 --> 00:01:50.160
He has strategic allies.

00:01:50.530 --> 00:01:52.750
Who do you become friends with?

00:01:52.750 --> 00:01:59.025
Who do you do business with versus who is an enemy of America?

00:01:59.560 --> 00:02:07.514
In doing so, people still look at him through the wrong lens.

00:02:08.291 --> 00:02:13.240
I come across very strong about some of the things I say.

00:02:13.680 --> 00:02:26.240
I truly believe when I told you what I was praying over about 'drinking the Kool-Aid' and the things I've said, because so many people only look at it as MAGA.

00:02:36.280 --> 00:02:41.959
I look at Trump as an instrument being used by the Lord.

00:02:42.623 --> 00:02:45.280
God doesn't make mistakes.

00:02:45.280 --> 00:02:55.000
I was sweeping out my car because I like to keep my stuff clean, and He said to me, 'Do you believe I make mistakes?

00:02:55.000 --> 00:03:02.954
' I want to ask you all a question: Do you believe that God makes mistakes in the decisions He makes?

00:03:07.540 --> 00:03:11.120
Do you believe you could be a mistake?

00:03:11.120 --> 00:03:17.430
Do you believe that everything God does is strategic?

00:03:29.267 --> 00:03:29.880
Are there mistakes in your existence or your personality?

00:03:29.880 --> 00:03:38.065
Do you think it's just by coincidence that you are who you are, or is God in everything?

00:03:38.065 --> 00:03:41.400
Does God have a hand in everything?

00:03:41.400 --> 00:03:48.080
Is God really that big that He knows every hair on your head?

00:03:48.080 --> 00:03:52.080
He knows your future better than you know your past.

00:03:53.172 --> 00:04:04.650
I saw that a lot of prophetic voices in the past have been very selective about how they relay things, like Brother Hagin.

00:04:07.647 --> 00:04:15.440
Brother Hagin would only say things that he was allowed to relay; the Holy Spirit would not allow him to share everything he received.

00:04:22.080 --> 00:04:28.171
But his personality, from what I experienced when I was in heaven, is very different.

00:04:28.171 --> 00:04:30.880
He was a very quiet individual.

00:04:32.907 --> 00:04:37.973
Even from that one encounter—and how much can you go by one encounter in heaven—when the Lord allowed me to have a visitation.

00:04:37.973 --> 00:04:45.360
I'm not talking to the dead; let the elevator go to the top.

00:04:45.360 --> 00:04:51.755
I had a visitation through a portal, allowing me to listen and talk to the living.

00:04:54.805 --> 00:04:56.227
They're not dead; they're alive.

00:04:56.227 --> 00:05:02.069
'I'm more alive now than I've ever been,' is what she said to me.

00:05:04.336 --> 00:05:05.472
I've processed this a lot.

00:05:14.700 --> 00:05:31.670
The Lord said, 'With the personality I have created in you over the course of your lifetime, do you think I made a mistake?

00:05:31.680 --> 00:05:37.640
' I said, 'No, you are a God who would never make a mistake.

00:05:37.640 --> 00:05:40.164
I'm fearfully and wonderfully made in Your image.

00:05:40.164 --> 00:05:47.440
' I know that every person here has a special call and has been chosen for such a time as this.

00:05:47.440 --> 00:05:55.760
Even if we do things stupidly, the footsteps of the righteous are ordered by the Lord.

00:05:55.760 --> 00:06:03.360
I believe that what the devil meant for bad, God will turn around for good and your favor immediately if you're seeking Him.

00:06:03.360 --> 00:06:05.960
You can't derail your life.

00:06:05.960 --> 00:06:16.120
No matter how bad you think you can mess it up, God will turn what the devil meant for bad into good if you are just seeking Him daily.

00:06:17.520 --> 00:06:22.067
Looking at my personality, I am very bold.

00:06:22.418 --> 00:06:25.128
I'm never going to back down from anything He tells me to say.

00:06:26.208 --> 00:06:31.440
Even if I'm hesitant, I say, 'Here I go, I'm going to jump.

00:06:31.440 --> 00:06:34.500
' I always tell my kids, 'Daddy's going to jump.

00:06:34.500 --> 00:06:42.920
' Even if it's not the popular opinion, I'm going to tell you what the Lord tells me.

00:06:45.591 --> 00:06:51.160
That's why I will never parrot other prophets.

00:06:51.160 --> 00:06:52.760
I don't parrot words.

00:06:52.760 --> 00:06:58.200
I hear what He tells me and say it with great boldness.

00:06:58.690 --> 00:07:06.360
It may mirror other prophetic words, but my words are not parroted.

00:07:06.360 --> 00:07:16.400
I'm not called to be part of an echo; I'm called to be a voice yielded to Him.

00:07:16.660 --> 00:07:20.000
I've asked Him many times if He wants me to say these things.

00:07:20.000 --> 00:07:28.503
He said that might have been the assignment for others back in the '50s through the '90s, but you are a 'closer.

00:07:28.503 --> 00:07:34.035
' Their assignment was for that generation; yours is different for your generation.

00:07:39.969 --> 00:07:47.400
You cannot compare your call or your ministry to theirs because they weren't called to say what you're called to say.

00:08:05.420 --> 00:08:11.280
Mirroring and comparing like a cookie cutter is to parrot.

00:08:11.493 --> 00:08:14.840
I've called you to stand out and be alone.

00:08:15.140 --> 00:08:20.800
You will say things that maybe even the elders don't think you should say.

00:08:22.540 --> 00:08:25.053
Fear only what I tell you to do.

00:08:25.053 --> 00:08:35.600
Do not worry; they are not accountable for your call, you will stand before Me concerning what I've asked you to do.

00:08:46.530 --> 00:08:52.200
To be a parrot is dangerous.

00:08:56.040 --> 00:09:03.760
Similarities are okay, but the Lord said people may parrot you, but you are to stand alone.

00:09:03.760 --> 00:09:09.300
Say what I tell you with accuracy and boldness, with visions that I give you.

00:09:09.610 --> 00:09:15.600
You'll see it in the news, and your channel will grow well over a million in the days ahead.

00:09:16.050 --> 00:09:19.200
I'll use you for My end-time glory.

00:09:21.720 --> 00:09:27.200
It's not always easy to stand alone, but I say what He tells me to say.

00:09:27.566 --> 00:09:31.120
I know I can miss it; I'm just human.

00:09:33.884 --> 00:09:36.729
If I miss it, I'll be the first to tell you.

00:09:37.120 --> 00:09:38.960
I have no pride in it.

00:09:43.846 --> 00:09:47.000
You humble yourself and keep moving.

00:09:51.445 --> 00:09:55.640
Anybody who says they've never missed it is a liar.

00:09:55.640 --> 00:09:57.269
I see people miss it all the time.

00:09:57.269 --> 00:10:01.770
I meet people who say, 'I don't ever miss it, Brandon.

00:10:01.770 --> 00:10:03.480
' It's called being human.

00:10:03.644 --> 00:10:08.660
I would love to meet some of the men in the Bible, like Isaiah and Jeremiah.

00:10:19.480 --> 00:10:20.080
They were awesome men of God, but we didn't see them as they were growing up or in their 20s.

00:10:23.590 --> 00:10:26.240
We don't have a glimpse of that.

00:10:26.240 --> 00:10:27.865
We know their strong points.

00:10:27.865 --> 00:10:31.240
We know the CliffNotes, the highlights.

00:10:31.240 --> 00:10:33.080
That's what the Bible tells us.

00:10:33.080 --> 00:10:34.580
It's like their Facebook highlight reel.

00:10:35.800 --> 00:10:37.380
I'm just being real with y'all.

00:10:37.600 --> 00:10:41.600
If they had a Facebook highlight reel, that's what we're reading.

00:10:41.600 --> 00:10:42.789
This is the best.

00:10:42.789 --> 00:10:43.086
Boom.

00:10:43.086 --> 00:10:43.943
And everybody's excited.

00:10:43.943 --> 00:10:47.800
But they don't see behind the scenes because Facebook doesn't show you that part, right?

00:10:47.800 --> 00:10:50.600
We don't know when people are having a bad day.

00:10:50.600 --> 00:10:51.571
We don't know their struggles.

00:10:51.571 --> 00:10:57.253
We don't know the depth of their relationship with the Lord because we didn't get to see that part.

00:10:57.253 --> 00:11:00.040
We got to see the highlight reel.

00:11:00.040 --> 00:11:03.720
And you can say that's blasphemous or whatever; it's the truth.

00:11:03.720 --> 00:11:07.080
We don't know everybody's flaws and everybody's stuff.

00:11:07.080 --> 00:11:07.875
You know why?

00:11:07.875 --> 00:11:10.783
Because we only see what the Lord allowed us to see.

00:11:10.783 --> 00:11:16.205
And through that passage of scripture, you don't know when they were down.

00:11:16.205 --> 00:11:22.920
You don't know what they went through in their marriages or their children or whatever.

00:11:22.920 --> 00:11:25.560
But everybody has a story.

00:11:25.560 --> 00:11:37.750
Everybody has a, b, c, d, and what you have from the day you were born to the day you die and what's in between the dashes.

00:11:37.760 --> 00:11:44.280
And so I separate myself as just a man.

00:11:44.280 --> 00:12:06.280
But as I pray and I tell you what I feel the Father has told me to tell you today—as I've prayed and interceded for America and what I see coming—I warned you what the Lord showed us concerning the economy and what I consider Trump's next plan.

00:12:07.160 --> 00:12:18.520
What did I tell you would happen if the Supreme Court ruled against him concerning the tariffs?

00:12:18.520 --> 00:12:21.600
I said he has a plan B.

00:12:21.600 --> 00:12:24.020
He's paddling as fast as he can in the canoe.

00:12:24.020 --> 00:12:25.920
Do you have the picture?

00:12:26.368 --> 00:12:28.160
Can you show them?

00:12:28.160 --> 00:12:34.760
He's paddling as fast as he can because I said he's trying to delay the inevitable.

00:12:34.760 --> 00:12:51.240
But in his mind, I said the economy is in trouble and there is no stopping this, right?

00:12:51.240 --> 00:12:51.425
Yeah.

00:12:51.425 --> 00:12:52.535
Say again.

00:12:52.535 --> 00:12:52.970
32 trillion.

00:12:53.345 --> 00:12:56.495
I don't know why when I switched back to it, it said 32 million.

00:12:57.726 --> 00:12:58.900
That's what it cut out.

00:12:59.095 --> 00:12:59.680
Say 32 trillion.

00:12:59.680 --> 00:13:00.360
Okay.

00:13:00.360 --> 00:13:01.947
So, do you hear what I'm saying?

00:13:01.947 --> 00:13:02.780
The 32 trillion.

00:13:02.780 --> 00:13:05.129
Please don't do that because I'm on a show and it's by the Holy Spirit.

00:13:05.129 --> 00:13:18.470
Now listen, I have to go back on my thoughts.

00:13:18.480 --> 00:13:19.836
32 trillion in the hole.

00:13:19.836 --> 00:13:24.777
And I saw Jerome Powell saying that basically America's economy is in trouble.

00:13:24.777 --> 00:13:35.011
And I said the Lord will anoint Trump to do this, and I saw a three-stranded cord and I saw things happening with Israel and things happening with America's economy.

00:13:35.011 --> 00:13:49.480
And so we see this photo right here where I warned you of all these major plans that I saw concerning Canada and Mexico and all this alliance.

00:13:49.480 --> 00:14:02.880
Well, I'm going to put everything together and we're going to go over things just a little bit for what I have seen in the last 24 hours.

00:14:02.880 --> 00:14:09.560
As I was praying into this weekend, the Lord showed me Iraq.

00:14:09.560 --> 00:14:12.380
How many people have I prayed over Iraq?

00:14:12.380 --> 00:14:15.280
I saw Iraq and there's military bases.

00:14:15.280 --> 00:14:17.147
There's great oil ties.

00:14:17.147 --> 00:14:27.940
There's things that are attached to Iraq from the United States government from when we invaded in the early 2000s because of the weapons of mass destruction and all the things.

00:14:27.940 --> 00:14:31.600
Remember, I saw the oil contracts.

00:14:31.600 --> 00:14:33.253
I saw a lot concerning this.

00:14:33.253 --> 00:14:44.560
But if you go back to what the Lord was showing us in this, I saw Iran being taken back to the stone age.

00:14:44.560 --> 00:14:52.880
But a lot of what the Lord showed me had to do with the tariffs.

00:14:52.880 --> 00:14:59.778
And when the Supreme Court justice came against the tariffs, I saw Trump saying, 'Well, it's time to do plan B.

00:14:59.778 --> 00:15:01.554
' And I said, 'That was war.

00:15:01.554 --> 00:15:02.251
' Remember that?

00:15:02.251 --> 00:15:07.240
That was clear back in February before they struck Iran.

00:15:07.240 --> 00:15:13.680
And I said, 'In the days ahead, they will strike Iran to combat what we see.

00:15:13.680 --> 00:15:16.008
' Do you have that video ready?

00:15:16.008 --> 00:15:16.471
Yeah.

00:15:19.220 --> 00:15:20.060
This one?

00:15:20.060 --> 00:15:20.480
Yep.

00:15:20.480 --> 00:15:29.190
You can play it if you want.

00:15:29.200 --> 00:15:30.560
If you can't, I'm going to keep talking.

00:15:30.560 --> 00:15:32.280
Okay.

00:15:32.587 --> 00:15:33.200
Go ahead.

00:15:36.920 --> 00:15:37.344
This will help.

00:15:37.344 --> 00:15:39.040
This was back in January.

00:15:42.720 --> 00:15:45.120
Hold on.

00:15:45.120 --> 00:15:50.550
Go ahead.

00:15:50.560 --> 00:15:52.440
Play it.

00:15:52.440 --> 00:16:08.920
'Allow the tariffs not to happen because that's the lifeblood of what the plan is concerning the economy of America, to allow the economy to flourish and to go to the next level.

00:16:25.129 --> 00:16:34.000
It would help sustain us and keep him paddling from going over the side of the waterfall because the economy was in trouble.

00:16:34.000 --> 00:16:42.533
' So, I've been praying over these tariffs because a plan B, if we don't have plan A, is the tariffs.

00:16:42.533 --> 00:16:48.280
Plan B is trying to scramble for what we can do to salvage the economy.

00:16:48.280 --> 00:17:01.920
How do we—if this falls and we have to pay back trillions of dollars to these countries and nations—what does America do with its economy?

00:17:01.920 --> 00:17:06.640
This is a very hard position with what's coming.

00:17:06.640 --> 00:17:16.880
And as I saw Greenland, I saw Venezuela, I saw the uprising of these—what Trump had a plan.

00:17:16.880 --> 00:17:31.040
Minerals, oil again, praying over Iran, the oil wells in Iran to be striking the oil wells in Iran to the BRICS nations.

00:17:31.040 --> 00:17:37.320
It's bigger than just the civilians on the ground doing this.

00:17:37.320 --> 00:17:39.549
This is much bigger than civilians.

00:17:39.549 --> 00:17:39.920
Why?

00:17:39.920 --> 00:17:41.460
Why did the civilians happen?

00:17:41.460 --> 00:17:44.920
