00:17:44.920 --> 00:17:46.400
How did that all happen?

00:17:46.400 --> 00:17:47.680
How did it get so big?

00:17:47.680 --> 00:17:50.200
It's much bigger than what I can say online.

00:17:50.200 --> 00:17:53.400
What will happen next?

00:17:53.400 --> 00:17:56.400
An escalation of war.

00:17:56.400 --> 00:18:03.773
I said if plan B doesn't take place—sorry, I saw plan B, and what was plan B?

00:18:05.955 --> 00:18:08.480
I said Iran's oil wells.

00:18:08.480 --> 00:18:09.627
How do you back the dollar?

00:18:09.627 --> 00:18:11.820
How do you bail yourself out?

00:18:11.820 --> 00:18:12.225
War.

00:18:12.225 --> 00:18:12.630
I saw war.

00:18:13.440 --> 00:18:21.440
I said World War III, Venezuela, Cuba, an escalation of things to stimulate the economy.

00:18:22.480 --> 00:18:23.851
What's the next phase?

00:18:23.851 --> 00:18:26.137
And I keep praying into this war.

00:18:26.137 --> 00:18:33.920
I saw the petrodollar going up, but I saw Iran's oil refineries being attacked.

00:18:38.740 --> 00:18:41.990
Remember those?

00:18:41.990 --> 00:18:51.560
That was all over the last several months of what I've warned you, and here we are today.

00:18:51.560 --> 00:18:58.413
So, what the Lord told us was that we're seeing that President Trump would attack Venezuela first.

00:18:58.413 --> 00:19:02.651
And I warned you how many times in videos: pray for Venezuela.

00:19:02.651 --> 00:19:03.029
I see Venezuela.

00:19:03.783 --> 00:19:14.560
I saw the oil wells and I said, 'He has to stop the agreement because I saw Venezuela and the guy with the slick black hair joining up with Russia.

00:19:14.560 --> 00:19:17.480
' And then they actually had the meeting.

00:19:17.480 --> 00:19:20.870
I was allowed to go to the meeting in the spirit.

00:19:20.870 --> 00:19:23.703
And I said parts of North Korea were there, Cuba was there.

00:19:24.251 --> 00:19:31.820
There were certain people that were in this meeting concerning the BRICS in Russia to try to destroy the dollar.

00:19:31.820 --> 00:19:34.472
And I said, 'I was allowed to go to this meeting.

00:19:34.472 --> 00:19:39.670
' Does anybody remember me telling you I went to the meeting in the spirit when I was praying?

00:19:39.670 --> 00:19:43.124
I was allowed to hear things that nobody else knew I was hearing.

00:19:43.124 --> 00:19:44.680
I was a fly on the wall.

00:19:44.680 --> 00:19:46.422
But the Lord allowed me to do this.

00:19:46.422 --> 00:19:47.640
Does anybody remember this?

00:19:47.640 --> 00:19:51.587
My son's shaking his head yes because he knows he's my scribe.

00:19:51.587 --> 00:19:54.840
But I love you, buddy.

00:19:54.840 --> 00:19:57.400
He's like, 'Yeah, I do remember this.

00:19:57.400 --> 00:20:02.464
' But I warned you about going to the meeting, and I went and I saw China.

00:20:02.464 --> 00:20:14.373
I saw all these major nations there, and Venezuela was the main target because they wanted the oil from Venezuela for them to back this.

00:20:14.373 --> 00:20:17.320
And then I saw I said Trump will go and attack there.

00:20:17.320 --> 00:20:21.411
And I warned—it's all on video—and I said it happened.

00:20:21.411 --> 00:20:21.726
Boom.

00:20:21.726 --> 00:20:23.533
They did it in the middle of the night.

00:20:23.533 --> 00:20:29.430
He didn't announce when he was going to do it.

00:20:30.880 --> 00:20:43.830
When does Trump ever announce his plan to the public and then follow through with it?

00:20:43.840 --> 00:20:46.640
I just want you all to be real right now.

00:20:46.640 --> 00:20:54.240
When has President Trump ever announced a plan and followed through with it very often?

00:20:54.240 --> 00:20:57.520
It's always a threat like a bully in the schoolyard, right?

00:20:57.520 --> 00:21:01.355
'You do this by this date or we're doing this.

00:21:01.355 --> 00:21:11.240
' And then he said, 'I would be really stupid as a president to tell you I'm going to attack them on Monday.

00:21:11.240 --> 00:21:13.000
' He said it right here.

00:21:13.000 --> 00:21:18.360
But everybody's like, 'Well, you know, we had a ceasefire agreement.

00:21:18.360 --> 00:21:23.700
We had Pakistan come through and deliver him all of a sudden.

00:21:23.700 --> 00:21:32.120
' So, President Trump is out there telling you when he's going to do what he's going to do, and you believe it.

00:21:32.120 --> 00:21:35.600
I'm just asking you, are you really that naive?

00:21:35.600 --> 00:21:43.211
He's not going to tell you whenever he's going to attack a country, telling you that we're going to go in there with guns blazing.

00:21:43.211 --> 00:21:44.785
We're going to blow up all the bridges.

00:21:44.785 --> 00:21:55.120
He's going to do it when he feels that the troops are safe—when the men and women putting their lives on the line are safe to do it.

00:21:55.120 --> 00:21:57.840
When he sees an opening.

00:21:57.840 --> 00:22:01.960
Did he tell you when he was going to attack Venezuela?

00:22:01.960 --> 00:22:10.840
He told you afterward, when the dude was in handcuffs walking across the ground in New York, going to go to his cell.

00:22:10.840 --> 00:22:16.040
We all knew afterward, but none of us knew when it was going to happen other than by the Spirit of God.

00:22:16.456 --> 00:22:22.700
I said within the next 48 hours he's going to attack Venezuela, and I told you exactly the date when it was going to happen.

00:22:22.700 --> 00:22:23.285
And guess what?

00:22:23.285 --> 00:22:24.760
It happened.

00:22:24.760 --> 00:22:28.400
That was only by the leading of the Holy Spirit.

00:22:28.400 --> 00:22:32.305
I said something major is going to happen within the next 24 hours.

00:22:36.409 --> 00:22:39.730
In the next 24 hours, we're going to see a major event take place.

00:22:39.960 --> 00:22:42.560
That was on New Year's Eve.

00:22:42.560 --> 00:22:43.560
I was interceding with y'all.

00:22:43.560 --> 00:22:45.920
And I told you something major is about to happen.

00:22:45.920 --> 00:22:48.711
On the third, he did what I said.

00:22:48.947 --> 00:22:51.020
I said, "It's so strong right now in the spirit.

00:22:51.020 --> 00:22:52.537
It feels like it's about to happen.

00:22:52.537 --> 00:22:53.394
" And guess what?

00:22:53.394 --> 00:22:55.740
Within that timeframe, the Lord said it, and it happened.

00:22:56.040 --> 00:23:03.000
I have it on video, and I'm trying to tell you what I see coming.

00:23:03.000 --> 00:23:15.640
